    dc:description "Figure 2. Allodorylaimus tuccitanus sp. nov. (Light Microscpy, ♀). (a–c) Anterior region in lateral median view. (d) Anterior genital branch. (e) Anterior region in lateral surface view. (f) Pharyngointestinal junction. (g) Entire. (h) Oviduct-uterus junction. (i–k) Vagina region. (l–o) Caudal region. Scale bars: a, b, i, l–o = 10 µm; c, j, k = 5 µm; d = 50 µm; g = 200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7859772/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

